metadata.name: Genesis Creator ID #1
metadata.description: Let the Creator games begin! MAJR Creators is the first video contest using NFTs. The top YouTube Creators earn ETH. Creator ID NFT holders submit videos into the contest using the MAJR YouTube browser extension. The Creators with the most votes earn ETH.  Creator IDs are built by MAJR DAO, the ultimate membership for content creators and their audiences. Learn how voters can earn ETH too.
